---
import '../index.css';
const pageTitle = 'Privacy Policy';
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{pageTitle} | JSON Compare Online</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Read the Privacy Policy for JSON Compare Online, our free JSON comparison tool that protects your data and maintains user trust."
    />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://comparejsononline.com/privacy-policy" />
    <script is:inline>
      (() => {
        const stored = localStorage.getItem('theme');
        const prefersDark = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
        if (stored === 'dark' || (!stored && prefersDark)) {
          document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
        }
      })();
    </script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:text-gray-100">
    <main class="min-h-screen mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 font-sans transition-colors duration-300">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-400">← Back to Home</a>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        JSON Compare Online respects your privacy. This page explains how we handle data when you use our json comparison tool, including what information is collected and how it is protected.
      </p>
      <section class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-900">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Data Collection</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          We do not store your JSON data permanently. JSON Compare Online is designed as a lightweight tool for comparing JSON online, and any content you paste is processed in your browser or transiently on the server only for the duration of your session.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-900">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          We may use minimal cookies or browser storage for theme preferences and user experience improvements. No personal data is tracked for advertising or third-party profiling.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="mt-8 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-900">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Security</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          We take security seriously. Our json compare utility does not collect sensitive personal information, and we follow best practices to keep the comparison experience safe for every user.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
